title: I Predicted the Collapse of a Billion Dollar Company
description:
Yesterday I reached out to Genesis, predicting their collapse. Instead of responding, they paused withdrawals and today I'm sharing what I found about Genesis Trading and why I believe they're insolvent.

Others would call it a Napoleon Hill pitch.
